overview:
Buybak offers Consumer to Business eCommerce Services to retailers and online sellers.

BuyBak offers retailers and online sellers websites with the ability to purchase online directly from consumers their no longer wanted consumer media (Books, CDs, DVDs, and Games) and Consumer Electronics (CellPhones, Digital Music Players/iPods, etc.) inventory for online/offline resale.

Consumers benefit with a single sale vs. the challenges associated with person-to-person, multiple online sales through eBay, Amazon and the like.

BuyBak provides its retail clients the online ability to purchase over 2.5M unique SKU’s of product directly from the largest inventory base in the world — consumers no longer wanted property. BuyBak provides the ability to set buyback prices through direct means, formula base or via data acquired through marketplaces like Amazon and others to ensure high resell margins. BuyBak also provides the ability to receive product in locatable warehouse setting, such that the retailer is able to efficiently to upload, sell, pick and ship committed product.
